# Database Conventions

- Drizzle schema source files live under `packages/db/src/schema`.
- Shared DB exports are surfaced from `packages/db/src/schema/index.ts` and `packages/db/src/index.ts`.
- Migrations and seed logic live in `packages/db`.

- When changing database code:
- update the source schema in `packages/db/src/schema`
- keep shared exports in sync when adding new schema files
- avoid placing application-specific request logic in the DB package

- Prefer extending existing table and enum patterns over introducing inconsistent schema styles.
